{"tid":1664376,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"五角大樓:中共計劃阻止美軍進駐全球關鍵港口","createTime":"2019-10-20T05:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T05:16:57.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fd55ec546bb9e07999346b82cbbd1540f4c0c3fe","tid":1664376,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T05:09:06.000Z","msg":"五角大樓:中共計劃阻止美軍進駐全球關鍵港口<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/10/19/a102689721.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2019%2F10%2F19%2Fa102689721.html&d=kavsisi6QTOS4EBqYfxwc7ScfX6drAaaDYLMstvIIS4%3D&h=c3f477b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/10/19/a102689721.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【新唐人北京時間2019年10月20日訊】美國官員和分析人士週四（10月17日）表示，中共打算阻止美軍使用全球具有戰略意義的港口。專家說，中共希望通過大力投資海外基礎設施項目來做到這一點。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據《華盛頓觀察家報》（The Washington Examiner）10月18日報導，週四，在美國眾議院運輸委員會聽證會上，首任專門負責中國事務的副助理國防部部長斯布拉吉亞（Chad Sbragia）表示，「他們（中共）的唯一願望是在全球範圍內提高自己的地位和能力」，這意味着，中共將擁有全球性軍事力量，而美國實際上可能沒有了安全港口。<br />\n<br />\n斯布拉吉亞擔心，中共會利用其經濟槓桿將美國海軍排除在前沿港口之外。他強調了自己的擔心&mdash;&mdash;如果美國在危機時試圖將軍隊部署到印太地區，中共國家主席習近平所提出的備受爭議的「一帶一路」旨在卻會利用經濟槓桿壯大中共軍隊的力量。<br />\n<br />\n斯布拉吉亞在證詞中表示，這看起來不像過去的做法，美國將不得不在全球行動，以便從一開始就在所有領域為自己及盟友競爭。<br />\n<br />\n中共國有企業正在世界各地的港口投資，這是習近平所堅持的所謂「海上絲綢之路」（Maritime Silk Road）的一部分。習近平聲稱，這「符合所有國家的利益」。川普政府將其視為「掠奪性」貸款計劃，因為中共通過向貧困國家貸款，獲得該國主要港口和鐵路的控制權。<br />\n<br />\n海岸警衛隊和海上運輸次委員會（Subcommittee for Coast Guard and Maritime Transportation.）共和黨領導人、俄亥俄州眾議員吉布斯（Bob Gibbs）表示，他對這些投資有兩方面擔憂。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">首先，這些資產具有商業和軍事雙重用途。第二，債務將使這些國家與中共聯繫在一起，從而有利於中共追求國際地位，並有可能抑制美國的海外行動。<br />\n<br />\n軍方官員表示贊同，他們認為，中共正試圖將美國人趕出全球航運瓶頸地區的港口。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"7124d4313484089828212d380dfa46befa3a80cc","tid":1664376,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T05:09:19.000Z","msg":"&lsquo;No safe harbors&rsquo;: China plots to block US military from key ports, Pentagon warns<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonexaminer.com/policy/defense-national-security/no-safe-harbors-china-plots-to-block-us-military-from-key-ports-pentagon-warns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonexaminer.com%2Fpolicy%2Fdefense-national-security%2Fno-safe-harbors-china-plots-to-block-us-military-from-key-ports-pentagon-warns&d=kavsisi6QTOS4EBqYfxwc7ScfX6drAaaDYLMstvIIS4%3D&h=127fbc53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonexaminer.com/policy/defense-national-security/no-safe-harbors-china-plots-to-block-us-military-from-key-ports-pentagon-warns</a>"},{"pid":"8ffb22995a680711154e176bd3dd0cd130b5d7d1","tid":1664376,"uid":280493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T05:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F7TDXL6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF7TDXL6.gif&h=773605eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64d2bd4e41f023be82ea3bf097dc8a6eeb272740","tid":1664376,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ffb22995a680711154e176bd3dd0cd130b5d7d1","tid":1664376,"uid":280493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T05:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F7TDXL6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF7TDXL6.gif&h=773605eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T05:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f3a3645685274c49985a17dee9c783b05de788","tid":1664376,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T05:16:57.000Z","msg":"中共想做咩根本就你知我知美國佬都知，咪當人傻先得架"}]}